# grapher_trace_implicit_circle_smoke.numos — Phase 10F/10G. Trace a general
# implicit contour.
#
# Commits "x^2+y^2=9" (a circle of radius 3) and walks the cursor AROUND the
# contour. Proves the predictor-corrector implicit tracer: it seeds an on-curve
# point in the viewport, then each `right` advances a fixed arc-length along the
# tangent (perpendicular to grad G) with a Newton correction back onto
# G(x,y)=lhs-rhs=0 — so the cursor stays ON the circle instead of showing nan or a
# fake y=0. LEFT/RIGHT walk opposite ways via a persistent heading.
#
# Phase 10G: the Graph tab opens directly in a CENTRED Trace for an implicit
# equation (no ENTER needed); ZOOM works while tracing (zooms about the control
# point); and the camera locks onto the cursor every step (syncViewportToCursor)
# so the circle scrolls under a cursor pinned to screen centre.
#
# Flow (src/apps/GrapherApp.cpp): seedImplicitTrace / correctOntoCurve /
# updateImplicitHeading / traceStep (Implicit). The circle plots via marching
# squares (plotImplicit) exactly as before.
#
# Warning-only: screenshot, NO golden, NOT CI-gated (absent from the
# generate-emulator-candidates CANDIDATES list and every emulator-build.yml step).
#
# Run:
#   program --headless --deterministic --script tests/emulator/scripts/grapher_trace_implicit_circle_smoke.numos \
#           --frames 800 --screenshot out/grapher_trace_implicit_circle_smoke.ppm --quiet
log "grapher_trace_implicit_circle: start"
wait 200
open_app Grapher
wait 60
# down -> Add row; enter -> edit slot 0; type "x^2+y^2=9" (right exits each exponent).
key down
key enter
key x
key ^
key 2
key right
key +
key y
key ^
key 2
key right
key =
key 9
key enter
wait 80
# Graph opens directly in a centred Trace for the implicit equation; ZOOM enlarges
# the circle while keeping the cursor centred, then each `right` walks the contour.
key graph
wait 80
key zoom
wait 60
key right
key right
key right
key right
key right
key right
wait 120
screenshot out/grapher_trace_implicit_circle_smoke.ppm
assert_app Grapher
log "grapher_trace_implicit_circle: walked the x^2+y^2=9 contour, cursor centred"
